original_result.completion_text:

Username: davidjl
Letters: d, a, v, i, d, j, l
Total Letters: 7

Therefore, the username "davidjl" consists of 7 letters. Remember, if there were additional constraints such as case sensitivity (e.g., differentiating between uppercase and lowercase), those would also be taken into account according to the specific rules provided. In this example, I assumed all letters are lowercase unless specified otherwise by the input.
